  <brief_title>Comparison of Two Vaginal Mesh Kits in the Management of Vaginal Prolapse</brief_title>
  <acronym>ELEPE</acronym>
  <official_title>A Prospective Comparison of Two Vaginal Mesh Kits in the Management of Anterior and Apical Vaginal Prolapse: Long Term-results for Apical Fixation and Quality of Life</official_title>
